{
  "texts": [
    "We employed certain parameters, such as precision, accuracy, recall, and the F1 score, to compare the performance of the PolynetDWTCADx system.",
    "These parameters play a fundamental role in evaluating the model's ability to classify colorectal conditions into distinct classes.",
    "Furthermore, we conducted a thorough comparison of the classification results, combining CNN with DWT and SVM, to determine the extent to which these two techniques enhance the classification accuracy.",
    "The U-Net model's semantic segmentation performance on the KvasirSeg dataset is analysed in these results.",
    "We employed the U-Net model to detect and segment polyps in the colon, and evaluated its performance using the IoU and the Dice coefficient."
  ]
}